graph TD
    A([Admin Clicks Generate]) --> B[Fetch active Courses, Rooms, Teachers from MySQL]
    B --> C[Flatten Data into Individual 1-Hour Sessions]
    C --> D[Apply MRV Heuristic: Sort queue by hardest-to-place sessions]
    D --> E{Are there Unplaced Sessions remaining?}
    E -- No Queue Empty --> F[Wipe old schedule & INSERT new schedule into MySQL]
    F --> G([Return Success to Dashboard])
    E -- Yes --> H[Select the most difficult Unplaced Session]
    H --> I[Scan the grid for Valid Slots that pass Hard Constraints]
    I --> J{Are Valid Slots Available?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Apply Soft Constraint Math to score available slots]
    K --> L[Lock Session into Highest-Scoring Slot]
    L --> E
    J -- No Dead End --> M[Trigger Recursive Backtracking]
    M --> N[Undo last previously placed Session]
    N --> O[Ban previous slot & Force it to take Alternative Slot]
    O --> E
